trans-unit.source: Indicates the progress of an operation.
A ProgressBar control consists of a window that is filled, by default from left to right, as an operation progresses.
trans-unit.target: ProgressBar 컨트롤, 왼쪽에서 오른쪽으로, 기본적으로 채워지는 작업이 진행 되는 창으로 구성 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The control has a range and a current position.
ProgressBar overrides the metadata of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A> property and sets its default to 100.
trans-unit.target: ProgressBar의 메타 데이터 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A>속성 및 해당 기본값 100으로 설정 합니다.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.RangeBase.Maximum%2A>

trans-unit.source: ProgressBar overrides the metadata of the <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A> property and sets its default to `false`.
trans-unit.target: ProgressBar의 메타 데이터 재정의 <xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>속성 해당 기본값을 설정 하 고 `false`.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement.Focusable%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Dependency Properties Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
Customizing the ProgressBar Control To apply the same property settings to multiple ProgressBar controls, use the <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 여러 개의 진행률 표시줄 컨트롤을 사용 하 여 동일한 속성 설정을 적용할의 ProgressBar 컨트롤을 사용자 지정의 <xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>속성.</xref:System.Windows.FrameworkElement.Style%2A>
